.DT
shoplift
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
shoplift

.SH peek - Used to covertly look at someone/something
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Syntax
peek [at] <object>
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Peek is the command to use when you want to look
at someone (or their things) without them noticing.

Your success is affected by your skill and whether you
are hiding or not.

.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> peek drunkard
> peek at dagger in drunkard

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
hide, sneak
.EP
